# Akses hosting & cPanel (Kaki Empat v2)

> **Stack v2:** PHP + MySQL self-hosted only â€” **no Firebase/FCM/BaaS**. Lihat rule `v2-stack-forbidden-services`.

## Lokasi kredensial (wajib dibaca dulu)

Semua kredensial server ada di:

**`.cursor/secrets/hosting.credentials`**

- Format INI (`[cpanel]`, `[mysql_v2]`, `[api_deploy]`, `[subdomains]`)
- Template tanpa rahasia: `.cursor/secrets/hosting.credentials.example`
- File `hosting.credentials` **di-gitignore** â€” jangan commit, jangan salin ke chat

Jika file ada dan terbaca, **jangan minta user username/password cPanel lagi**. Langsung pakai nilai dari file.

## Login cPanel

1. URL: nilai `cpanel.url` (default `https://kakiempat.com:2083`)
2. User / password: dari section `[cpanel]`
3. **Satu percobaan login**, jeda antar langkah (risiko blokir IP jika terlalu cepat/berulang)
4. Opsi otomasi: browser MCP â†’ navigate â†’ isi form â†’ login sekali

## MySQL v2 (aplikasi & API)

Gunakan section `[mysql_v2]` untuk:

- `lib/core/config/env_config.dart` / dart-define
- `.env` lokal (salin dari `.env.example`)
- `hosting_v2/api/.mysql_v2.php` di server (jangan commit)

## Deploy & verifikasi

| Tugas | Referensi |
|--------|-----------|
| Paket API lokal | `scripts/deploy_api.ps1` â†’ `build/deploy_api` |
| Deploy git (no FTP) | `scripts/deploy_git.ps1` â†’ commit â†’ `git push` |
| Owner BFF saja | `scripts/deploy_api_owner.ps1` (lihat rule `deploy-workflow`) |
| Build Flutter web | `scripts/deploy_web.ps1 -WebRenderer html -Target owner` |
| Picu cPanel manual | `scripts/trigger_cpanel_deploy.ps1` |
| Docroot API | `api_deploy.docroot` |
| Cek API hidup | `curl` ke `api_deploy.health_url` |
| Migrasi SQL | `api_deploy.migrate_url?secret=...&file=001_core_tables.sql` |
| Kosongkan DB v2 | `scripts/db/truncate_kakiempa_v2.sql` / `scripts/truncate_v2_database.ps1` |

Subdomain aktif: lihat `[subdomains]` di `hosting.credentials` / `.example`.

## Arsitektur 6 subdomain

| Subdomain | Fungsi | Target pengguna | Deploy / kode |
|-----------|--------|-----------------|---------------|
| `www.kakiempat.com` | Landing & marketing (layanan, harga, testimoni, blog, form daftar owner/sitter) | Visitor, calon pengguna | `scripts/deploy_web.ps1 -Target www` â†’ docroot `public_html` |
| `owner.kakiempat.com` | Dashboard pemilik hewan (profil hewan, booking, jadwal, transaksi, ulasan) | Pet owner (login) | `deploy_web.ps1 -Target owner`; `WebDomain.owner` + `AuthGate` â†’ `OwnerHomePage` |
| `sitter.kakiempat.com` | Dashboard pengasuh (ketersediaan, terima/tolak booking, laporan, profil) | Pet sitter (login) | `deploy_web.ps1 -Target sitter`; `WebDomain.sitter` â†’ `SitterLandingPage` |
| `admin.kakiempat.com` | Panel admin (verifikasi sitter, booking, transaksi, laporan, pengaturan) | Admin / operator | `deploy_web.ps1 -Target admin`; `WebDomain.admin` + `AuthGate` â†’ `AdminPanelPage` |
| `staging.kakiempat.com` | Uji coba frontend terisolasi (branch/DB staging, bukan production) | Developer, QA | `deploy_web.ps1 -Target staging`; `WebDomain.staging` (AuthGate owner) |
| `api.kakiempat.com` | REST API stateless (auth, user, booking, pet, payment, notifikasi, review) | Hanya frontend (bukan user langsung) | `scripts/deploy_api.ps1`; `EnvConfig.apiBaseUrl`; docroot `[api_deploy]` |

Infrastruktur: SSL wildcard `*.kakiempat.com`; routing NGINX reverse proxy; API dapat di-scale horizontal.

Deteksi host web: `lib/core/web/domain_router.dart` (hostname â†’ `WebDomain`).

## Keamanan

- Jangan ulangi password penuh di respons chat ke user
- Jika kredensial bocor/rotasi, update hanya `hosting.credentials` (dan password di cPanel)
